						               													<description>THARKAD ABLAZE&amp;#10;Seat of power for the Lyran people since 2407, the frozen shores of Tharkad have sparkled with the might of the merchant princes of House Steiner for centuries.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Then came the Jihad.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Jihad Turning Points: Tharkad fleshes out the details of the conflict surrounding this pivotal world published in various Jihad Plot Sourcebooks. Additionally, players can join one of the myriad of forces fighting for control--and survival--of House Steiner's seat of power.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This campaign series uses the Chaos Campaign rules and gives players the option of fighting individual battles, following a campaign arc, inserting it into their own campaigns and even create their own scenarios with optional rules to give their games a &amp;circ;_&amp;Ntilde;??Tharkad flavor.&amp;circ;? The ebook includes a detailed map of the world of Tharkad, a run down of the forces involved in the conflict, and several tracks that players can use to run simple lance-on-lance battles, or stage up to a world-wide invasion. Only the players' imaginations are the limits.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
